Package: MapAccuracy
Type: Package
Title: Assess the accuracy of remotely sensed maps
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Alber Sanchez
Maintainer: Alber Sanchez <albhasan@gmail.com>
Description: Compute an assessment of the accuracy of remotely sensed change 
    maps using the area of each class in the map. The assesment is based on the 
    good practices proposed by Pontus Olofsson.
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Imports:
    methods,
    roxygen2,
    testthat
